the Department for Local Government budget unit to be distributed to the City of Erlanger to support the Eons
Adventure Park initiative.
Section 276. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of $1,000,000 in fiscal year
2026-2027 and $500,000 in fiscal year 2027-2028 from the Budget Reserve Trust Fund Account established in KRS
48.705 to the Kentucky Infrastructure Authority budget unit to be distributed to the City of Harlan to support water
and sewer upgrades.
Section 277. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of $1,300,000 in each
