2027-2028 from the Budget Reserve Trust Fund Account established in KRS 48.705 to the Department for Local
Government budget unit to be distributed to the Daviess County Fiscal Court to support the Green River Community
Food warehouse project.
Section 281. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of $60,000 in fiscal year
2026-2027 from the Budget Reserve Trust Fund Account established in KRS 48.705 to the Department for Local

