KRS 48.705 to the Department for Local Government budget unit to be distributed to the Lincoln County Fiscal
Court to support economic development as it relates to water, sewer, and infrastructure. Funds shall not be expended
on roads.
Section 284. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of $2,500,000 in each
