2026-2027 from the Budget Reserve Trust Fund Account established in KRS 48.705 to the Department for Local
Government budget unit to be distributed to the City of Stanton, in collaboration with the Stanton Parks and
Recreation Board, for infrastructure and associated equipment needs at the Stanton city park.
Section 290. There is hereby appropriated General Fund moneys in the amount of $3,000,000 in fiscal year
2027-2028 from the Budget Reserve Trust Fund Account established in KRS 48.705 to the Kentucky Infrastructure
Authority budget unit to be distributed to the Western Rockcastle Water District to support the water infrastructure
upgrades.
